					</div>
					<div class="col s12 l1 center hide-on-med-and-down" style="padding-top:48px">
						<img src="img/pointer.png" width="48px">
					</div>
					<div class="col s12 m3 l2 center">
						<img src="img/step3.png" width="120px">
						<h5 class="center">Send data</h5>
						<p>ส่งข้อมูลเข้าสู่ Server</p>
					</div>
					<div class="col s12 l1 center hide-on-med-and-down" style="padding-top:48px">
						<img src="img/pointer.png" width="48px">
					</div>
					<div class="col s12 m3 l2 center">
						<img src="img/step4.png" width="120px">
						<h5 class="center">Explore</h5>
						<p>ดูผลข้อมูลที่ส่งเข้ามาในแบบ Real time</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="parallax-container valign-wrapper">
			<div class="section no-pad-bot">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="row center">
						<h5 class="header col s12 light">Powerful platform for visualize your IoT data</h5>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="parallax"><img src="img/powerful.jpg" alt="Unsplashed background img 3"></div>
